snippet.title: Ezra Miller FIRED from The Flash?! Amber Heard is a FAKER?!
snippet.description:
It's DCEU drama! Could Ezra Miller be fired from his role as The Flash? There's a rumor that Warner execs aren't happy with the publicity of him slamming a fan in Iceland. And did Amber Heard FAKE evidence? Will she get fired... or WORSE?
